	- [incompatible change] Rename 'title' option to 'caption'.

        - Follow newer Text::Table::Tiny interface (exportable 'generate_table'
          function).

	- [Text::Table::Org backend] Pass 'caption' option.

	- [doc] Describe interfaces differences with Text::Table::Tiny (list of
          unsupported options).

        - [doc] Tweak Synopsis.


